    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed per MRL 2 scoping. Validation results demonstrate RHI prediction error of 4.2% MAE against bench measurements, satisfying the < 10% acceptance criterion. The credibility body of evidence is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device. Note: validation runs were executed under solver configuration 2024-q3-build-2; the current model of record is 2026-q1-build-7. The assessment team considers this acceptable pending re-verification of the updated build.",
